{"tid":2410371,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"房協斥2,000萬裝W形喉","createTime":"2021-02-16T14:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T22:28:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"85ffacddf2f99573e87b1120a1b47b76a374bacf","tid":2410371,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:16:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210216/MO2EA7BXIRAMTKVLBCZTB53VVE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210216%2FMO2EA7BXIRAMTKVLBCZTB53VVE%2F&d=2uuoLuAEMU6cBVSXjgSp%2BZmjxQ%2Bt9FMRZQKIc78GZWw%3D&h=43828898\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210216%2FMO2EA7BXIRAMTKVLBCZTB53VVE%2F&h=d50828f5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210216/MO2EA7BXIRAMTKVLBCZTB53VVE/</a><br />\n<br />\n房協斥2,000萬裝W形喉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vNUdw77_Z_0WpD4zeH6fZ2V9vOY=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Y36SZOIRBJBFFIY35XL3XNHD3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvNUdw77_Z_0WpD4zeH6fZ2V9vOY%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FY36SZOIRBJBFFIY35XL3XNHD3U.jpg&h=e3957fa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■莫太的祖堯邨單位廁所改裝W形喉管，洗澡時可為喉管注水，避免病毒散播。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】武漢肺炎持續， 大廈喉。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：地盤、食肆、復業處所 職員均須驗毒  檢測爆滿 放假頻撲為返工<br />\n<br />\n莫太一家四口在荔景祖堯邨住了四年，她指過往沒有為U形管注水，惟自去年青衣長康邨發生懷疑單位廁所喉管播毒事件，她即開始每周為廁所U形喉管注入清水或漂白水，惟有時會忘記注水。房協去年底為其單位洗手間的U形管改裝為W形管後，她便毋須再擔心忘記注水問題。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n升降機加感應器 隔空㩒𨋢<br />\n<br />\n房協指祖堯邨洗手間分為淋浴間和地台，分別接駁兩條U形水管，其中接駁地台的U形管，若住戶不是經常洗地，喉管有可能乾涸，需要定期注水。<br />\n<br />\n新安裝的W形聚水器取代兩個U形管，只要住戶洗澡，即能同時為淋浴間和地台喉管注水。W形管亦可連接洗手盆和鋅盆，每當居民用水，水就能自動流向地台的W形管，確保聚水器長期有水。<br />\n<br />\n房協指，首階段為健康村一期和祖堯。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n另外，為減少居民觸摸公用設施，。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"a434a7d8091684fdac6efac5ec239822b8a7dec0","tid":2410371,"uid":156363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:22:17.000Z","msg":"會唔會好易塞？"},{"pid":"65c8fa193e6e00f9ab70a243588d75663aac9edc","tid":2410371,"uid":178875,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"2000萬大判食1900萬 <br />\n100萬二判搞掂<br />\n<br />\n然後話唔夠錢追加3000萬<br />\n但係都係食曬 做舊屎出黎<br />\n<br />\n最後扮調查但冇人要負責<br />\n再用多5000萬監察還原再安裝<br />\n<br />\n前前後後起碼億幾同三五七年"},{"pid":"60073eaa28cce5e5e00dc442548d91b2c19f3cd7","tid":2410371,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:47:44.000Z","msg":"咁既喉會唔會好易穿或裂？"},{"pid":"667fcfb75194aee7e79091cc33dd711339420acc","tid":2410371,"uid":281822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65c8fa193e6e00f9ab70a243588d75663aac9edc","tid":2410371,"uid":178875,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"2000萬大判食1900萬 <br />\n100萬二判搞掂<br />\n<br />\n然後話唔夠錢追加3000萬<br />\n但係都係食曬 做舊屎出黎<br />\n<br />\n最後扮調查但冇人要負責<br />\n再用多5000萬監察還原再安裝<br />\n<br />\n前前後後起碼億幾同三五七年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:15:45.000Z","msg":"房協食自己喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n房委會先可以無限追加<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c38223cc5bbf6ad84fc27188349f875ca3d469f3","tid":2410371,"uid":64073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"667fcfb75194aee7e79091cc33dd711339420acc","tid":2410371,"uid":281822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"65c8fa193e6e00f9ab70a243588d75663aac9edc","tid":2410371,"uid":178875,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"2000萬大判食1900萬 <br />\n100萬二判搞掂<br />\n<br />\n然後話唔夠錢追加3000萬<br />\n但係都係食曬 做舊屎出黎<br />\n<br />\n最後扮調查但冇人要負責<br />\n再用多5000萬監察還原再安裝<br />\n<br />\n前前後後起碼億幾同三五七年"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T15:15:45.000Z","msg":"房協食自己喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><b